: false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "很清淡。调理除了盐，全都是自己种的草。<br><br>我原来也以为这样的食物会不好吃。但是后来知道，清淡其实是有食物的真味的。当季的茄子，番茄，西葫芦…混合了薄荷，九层塔…每个味道都纯粹，但混和在一起，既单纯，又微妙丰富，富于变幻。意想不到的美味，浑浊的重味了反而掩盖了它真正的美感。<br><br>人格大抵也是如此吧。<br><br><br>谢谢作者告诉了我这么清新易懂却难以发现的道理💜", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "悦纳echo", "author_id": "b87530d14bea057eba5ee76fca58ddf3", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "chen-lan-15-64", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "498833067", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "498833067", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "那男孩是你之前讲到的小公主吗", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "沉澜", "author_id": "e5ffee36c1337b0c253b2461fae4eabc", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "wanlihongxia", "headline": "律师", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "9961109124", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "9961109124", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "十多年前从湖北来广东这里，发现这里食物真是寡淡难吃，十年后吃不下复杂的食物。吃桃，只喜欢纯粹的桃子味道，可惜基本买不到；吃鸡肉，不戴腥味的走地鸡，过水除血腥味，白切最能体现鸡肉的鲜美，盐焗也不错，咸香；海鲜最是不用说了。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "wanlihongxia", "author_id": "d502ee5a9d78295916c577912901b6ec", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "mi-ao-54-74", "headline": "外表像猫，内心像老虎！即要好看的皮囊，也要有趣的灵魂！ ", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "957714126", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "957714126", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "这才是用心的答案，感觉比几个高赞好多了", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "咪ao", "author_id": "0b7f1687a68a211d93c63c67e939c9bc", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "wang-xu-2", "headline": "专注青少年心理健康30年", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "810560683", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "810560683", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>四川口音的法语我tm笑死，日常辱髮（1/1）</p>", "like_count": 0, "au